To throw the diamond loser, you hope spades split 3-3 and lead out 3 rounds.  The third round gets ruffed low by RHO and you must overruff.  Back to dummy with the Ace of clubs, playing a fourth round of spades hoping RHO had a singleton trump. No luck. RHO ruffs again and you overruff again.  Now the only trump outstanding is the Ace so you can return to dummy with a club ruff and lead out the fifth spade, throwing your diamond loser.|
